- "Average rating greater than 4.0" means the movies have received a high average rating from users.

sql:
SELECT COUNT(user_id) AS num_users_with_higher_avg_rating
FROM user_activity
WHERE avg_rating > (SELECT AVG(avg_rating) FROM user_activity);

