sql:
SELECT user_id, total_movies_watched
FROM user_activity
ORDER BY total_movies_watched DESC;

external_knowledge:
- Positive ratings are those greater than 3 on a scale of 1-5;
- Negative ratings are those less than 3 on a scale of 1-5;
- The weighted average rating combines the movie's average rating with a rating derived from the distribution of positive and negative reviews.

- "shining star" refers to the user with the highest average rating;
- "movie enthusiasts" refers to users who have rated movies;
- "favorite movie picks" refers to the recommended movies for the user.
